tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"部隊鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9f8e1163f58d7af23f5354d5f606eb90dd4b56","tid":410620,"uid":147972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"B仔雞翼囉<br />\n絲有無食過？"},{"pid":"111a0fc0000a94f96cac75f6512e6466434b6ed3","tid":410620,"uid":135645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"賽螃蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd70af72aa7862e672645184d2d7466bdf226491","tid":410620,"uid":128930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:30:20.000Z","msg":"糖醋排⻣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知錦煮啱唔啱，係老母傳授加我自己風格<br />\n腩排洗淨，糖，豉油，生抽，老抽，濕粉，胡椒粉，酒，薑粒，蒜頭切碎，求撚其醃一陣<br />\n中大火燒熱油，<br />\n落薑，聞到味就落排骨，煎到金金黃黄<br />\n灒酒，兜兜佢，落冰糖，鎮江醋，(我自己鐘意加小小白米醋)<br />\n煮一煮先，加水岩岩好蓋過d肉就得，煮滾就轉細火，可以加兩粒八角(我覺得浸味好正)<br />\n細火炆45分鐘，睇下夠唔夠腍，唔夠就加多十分鐘<br />\n確認夠腍，開蓋開大火收汁，煮到傑傑地就得，照計唔洗落生粉水，食得<br />\n<br />\n可能同出面食有d唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都幾好味，可以試下"},{"pid":"d43fd6c062f65d2f8405e63f9369467bcf2ff8fb","tid":410620,"uid":60357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"瑤柱節瓜甫"},{"pid":"d56ec0ad2c87f2be9c4e46354078669fa5cb8c59","tid":410620,"uid":20892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/23/221553_0367d411c68646bcbf400c24cfd50def.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F221553_0367d411c68646bcbf400c24cfd50def.jpg&h=eb1fbc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生菜魚肉"},{"pid":"528f218e133c2499345b6a6feeeec0022c535775","tid":410620,"uid":8719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"心意嘅野都諗住取巧 唔做好過做"},{"pid":"1be29ae1132a3c3ad9662a89b9863b27d4835005","tid":410620,"uid":6590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:26:17.000Z","msg":"落雨炒蛋"},{"pid":"ace1324e7b84883390db324abd775205ddb0bf23","tid":410620,"uid":15807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"鹽燒鯖魚<br />\n去買急凍嘅，解凍之後用廚紙吸乾少少水<br />\n加鹽用平底鑊慢火煎，皮果面落先煎耐啲先好反，唔係會爛。<br />\n切半個檸檬，食之前落啲檸檬汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加一碗白飯正曬<br />\n仲可以買沖嘅麵豉湯，諗起都餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c059a68c1ae0bb504e106b30ccad3509b29a0613","tid":410620,"uid":15807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蒸水蛋<br />\n我覺得哩個易得黎<br />\n上面平就已經好靚又好味<br />\n鍾意ge 加條蔥倒d 豉油<br />\n3隻蛋加一盒細屎暈新清支湯<br />\n搞勻倒落隻碟<br />\n係咁2篤走氣泡<br />\n笠保鮮紙/鍚紙/搵隻碟反轉<br />\n拎去蒸就得<br />\n未衰過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n煮咩都好，頭一兩次實有啲fail<br />\n試多幾次先好黎真"},{"pid":"1c7c5c21a3a93322146718998cf92ed2a1ac52b2","tid":410620,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>B仔雞翼囉<br />\n絲有無食過？</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但上網睇過好似好多材料好多步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53af7f808c6369122be1c1ebe4f8157f727e378","tid":410620,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>糖醋排⻣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知錦煮啱唔啱，係老母傳授加我自己風格<br />\n腩排洗淨，糖，豉油，生抽，老抽，濕粉，胡椒粉，酒，薑粒，蒜頭切碎，求撚其醃一陣<br />\n中大火燒熱油，<br />\n落薑，聞到味就落排骨，煎到金金黃黄<br />\n灒酒，兜兜佢，落冰糖，鎮江醋，(我自己鐘意加小小白米醋)<br />\n煮一煮先，加水岩岩好蓋過d肉就得，煮滾就轉細火，可以加兩粒八角(我覺得浸味好正)<br />\n細火炆45分鐘，睇下夠唔夠腍，唔夠就加多十分鐘<br />\n確認夠腍，開蓋開大火收汁，煮到傑傑地就得，照計唔洗落生粉水，食得<br />\n<br />\n可能同出面食有d唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都幾好味，可以試下</blockquote><br />\n好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5a2373eafe48aecc8373b939c502983b4e9382","tid":410620,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鹽燒鯖魚<br />\n去買急凍嘅，解凍之後用廚紙吸乾少少水<br />\n加鹽用平底鑊慢火煎，皮果面落先煎耐啲先好反，唔係會爛。<br />\n切半個檸檬，食之前落啲檸檬汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加一碗白飯正曬<br />\n仲可以買沖嘅麵豉湯，諗起都餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正吖我好鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7286886a42af46d4905f8c4a25d479869462518b","tid":410620,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蒸水蛋<br />\n我覺得哩個易得黎<br />\n上面平就已經好靚又好味<br />\n鍾意ge 加條蔥倒d 豉油<br />\n3隻蛋加一盒細屎暈新清支湯<br />\n搞勻倒落隻碟<br />\n係咁2篤走氣泡<br />\n笠保鮮紙/鍚紙/搵隻碟反轉<br />\n拎去蒸就得<br />\n未衰過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n煮咩都好，頭一兩次實有啲fail<br />\n試多幾次先好黎真</blockquote><br />\n知道 我會練下先了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953f517ee2b8d185c